originalText.text: These ladies are my go-to wash and fold professionals! They always clean my clothes very well and are so nice. I also got a dress hemmed for a very decent price and it looked great. Highly recommend them!

originalText.text: I find that many of the 1 star reviews this place has gotten are not exactly that… when rating 1-5 and you find someone saying “they were late the customer is always right” and gives them a 1 star you get their frustrations but that low of a score was not warranted. I have sent my items to be tailored many of times and they have met the deadline time and time again. I have asked for things to be cleaned sooner than most locations would ever entertain and they have made it happen. Will there be a time they’ll miss a certain window, I’m sure of it if you asked for an unrealistic window but they do make the effort this much I’ve experienced so far through a year and a half of being a customer here. Also the hours posted in a picture a customer put up is incorrect, that was their pandemic hours of 8-5pm now it’s 8-6:30pm mon-Friday and Saturday 8-6pm.

originalText.text: Always very friendly and quick service. It’s easy and convenient. I have used them several times now and will continue. I even have laundry in my apartment and still choose to take my laundry here because it’s easier.

originalText.text: Great and reliable. Always on time and are able to remove hard to get stains. Have been using their services for over 2 years now and don’t see changing them unless I move. Their wash and fold service is reasonably priced, but we mostly used them for dry cleaning. No complaints. All praise!
